A PACKAGE DEAL
WAK-11
PRIORITY
WHEN YOU NEED IT THERE TODAY
Just bring your "WISK-IT" package to any Wings West
Airlines ticket counter at least 30 minutes before the
desired flight. We will "WISK-IT" to its destination with
care. Then, just 10 minutes atter the flight s arrival, your
"WISK-IT" package is available for pick-up at the
destination Wings West ticket counter, except in San
Francisco where "WISK-IT" packages are available at
the American Airlines baggage facilities and San Jose
where they can be picked up at Air Cal's baggage
facilities.
In fact, Wings West Airlines can have your "WISK-IT"
package arrive in nearly any city in the country within
hours. You can specify the connecting flights, just by
checking with a Wings West ticket agent.
